description:
Row echelon form, reduced row echelon form, rank computation, nullspace basis, LU decomposition with partial pivoting.

Generic over `F: FiniteField`, with specialized kernels dispatched via `FieldBackend` for performance-critical inner loops.

## Operations

```rust
impl<F: FiniteField> FieldMatrix<F> {
    pub fn rref(&self) -> (FieldMatrix<F>, Vec<usize>);
    pub fn rank(&self) -> usize;
    pub fn nullspace(&self) -> Vec<FieldVec<F>>;
    pub fn lu(&self) -> (FieldMatrix<F>, FieldMatrix<F>, Vec<usize>);
}
```

- `rref` — RREF with pivot columns
- `rank` — via RREF or LU
- `nullspace` — basis vectors of the kernel
- `lu` — PA = LU decomposition with partial pivoting

## Dependencies

- FieldMatrix dense type (ab791e27)
